Definition: seen in the mind as a mental image
Example: the glory of his envisioned future; the snow-covered Alps pictured in her imagination; the visualized scene lacked the ugly details of real life
Synonyms: pictured, visualized, visualised, seen, in, the, mind, as, a, mental, image, glory, of, his, future, snow-covered, Alps, her, imagination, scene, lacked, ugly, details, real, life
Category: adj.all
